      "Shortness of Breath: Difficulty breathing during physical exertion or at rest, often accompanying chest pain.",
      "Fatigue: Unusual tiredness or a feeling of exhaustion during routine activities.",
      "Nausea: Sometimes, individuals may experience nausea or an upset stomach."
